&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree or equivalent practical experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;7 years of experience in sales management or operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5 years of experience using data analytics tools (e.g., Google Sheets or spreadsheet software), Salesforce, or a Customer Relationship Management (CRM) tool to measure sales performance or operational challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3 years experience leading a Door to Door sales channel.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 year of experience in multi-dwelling property sales.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;It&#39;s preferred if you have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Direct experience building, managing, and retaining Sales teams in the telecom industry.&lt;/li&gt;
