&lt;p&gt;GFiber is expanding into new markets and the CPE Supply Chain Program Manager plays a key part in supporting that expansion strategy. This role will be responsible for supporting sales, inventory and operational planning (SIOP) activities for customer premise and network engineering equipment.&lt;/p&gt;
