&lt;li&gt;Lead cross-functional GTM strategies designed for long, complex enterprise sales cycles with high-touch sales enablement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop specialized fulfillment orchestration, service management, and service assurance processes for the enterprise segment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive revenue growth, margin optimization, and market share for commercial portfolio; develop robust business cases for network and product investments and development efforts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
