&lt;p&gt;As a GFiber Webpass Hybrid Technician, you will build, troubleshoot, upgrade, and maintain our Network. Every building is different so you&#39;ll bring a wide variety skill set, exercise solid judgment, and collaborate well as a team. After a building is on the network customers will need to have service installed in their unit. You&#39;ll provide a fast and friendly customer experience during the installation process. For most of our customers you will be the only GFiber employee they ever meet, so you will not be just a skilled technician, but a brand ambassador.&lt;/p&gt;
