&lt;li&gt;Maintain a healthy funnel built upon a variety of promotional activities (e.g. cold calling, prospecting, mailers, warm follow-ups, and networking).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support cross functional teams in coordinating and conducting site surveys and customer acquisition tasks as requested by the Head of Sales.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At a minimum we&#39;d like you to have:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
