&lt;li&gt;2 years of experience with contracts or access agreements working cross-functionally.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2 years of experience with funnel management in a 30 to 90 day sale cycle.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Valid Driver’s License.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to pass a motor vehicle check that meets company standards.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
