&lt;p&gt;In this role, you will lead the engineering behind GFiber&#39;s nationwide multi-terabit backbone owning reliability, capacity planning, observability, and automation across a multi-vendor backbone. This is a senior technical role with team leadership responsibilities: you&#39;ll set technical direction for a small team of network engineers while staying hands-on in design and code.&lt;/p&gt;
